\s Yesu, Muchungaji wetu mwema
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu, Muchungaji wetu mwema, utuchunge siku zote, Utulishe sisi kundi lako na chakula cha milele.\bd*\bd  {\bd*\bd Bwana Yesu, Bwana Yesu, sisi wako, utuchunge\bd*\bd .} x2\bd*
